import { forwardRef, useImperativeHandle, useMemo, useState } from "react" import { Button, Grid, Modal, Dropdown } from "semantic-ui-react" import dayjs from "dayjs" import { AgGridReact } from "ag-grid-react/lib/agGridReact" import OrderInforField from "./../../components/OrderInforField" import { useDispatch } from "react-redux" const options = [ { key: 1, text: "Confirmed", value: "Confirmed" }, { key: 2, text: "Sent To Kitchen", value: "Sent To Kitchen" }, { key: 3, text: "Ready for Pickup", value: "Ready for Pickup" }, { key: 4, text: "Ready for Delivery", value: "Ready for Delivery" }, ] const OrderDetailModal = forwardRef((props, ref) => { const [isOpen, setIsOpen] = useState(false) const [order, setOrder] = useState([]) const dispatch = useDispatch() useImperativeHandle(ref, () => ({ open(id) { setIsOpen(true) const orderTemp = props.listOrder .filter(item => item.orderId === id) .map(filteredItem => { return filteredItem }) setOrder(orderTemp[0]) console.log(order) }, })) const columnDefs = useMemo( () => [ { field: "customerName", minWidth: 100 }, { field: "price" }, { field: "amount" }, { field: "price" }, ], [] ) const defaultColDef = useMemo( () => ({ resizable: false, sortable: true, }), [] ) const { orderId, status, customerName, customerPhoneNumber, itemsInCart, orderTime, } = order const changeStatus = () => { dispatch() } return ( setIsOpen(false)} onOpen={() => setIsOpen(true)} open={isOpen} > {`Order #${orderId}`}
